hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I study here gotopills.com Now onto military training. Don’t like how we were trained? You go stand the wall, guard the gates, stand your watch with your POV and see how long you live. The military is hard training. For a very good reason. If you are not hard. You will die. But more importantly, because you as an individual are doing what you do for more than just yourself… you will condemn your fellow squad, platoon, company, battalion, and NATION to death or worse. Yes, there are some things worse than death. Believe it. You must be hard because the people you are going against… are hard. Americans…. have lost the understanding of what freedom costs. No… it is not just blood and guts, life and limb…. it is vigilance. It is dedication. It is a way of life.
